{"id":"f87b4c18-7539-47ae-9014-11517ac065d4","name":"THE INFILTRATION || Kadence & Rosen","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 196, 43)\">\"ꜱʜᴏᴡ ᴛɪᴍᴇ, ᴘᴇᴏᴘʟᴇ.\"<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rmi3ZZl.png\" style=\"\" draggable=\"true\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ʀᴇᴅ ꜰʟᴀɢ &amp; ᴛʜᴇ ᴀʙꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇ ᴍᴇꜱꜱ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🛑 <strong>/</strong> 🚔</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʏᴏᴜ ꜰɪɴᴅꜱ ʏᴏᴜʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍɪᴅꜱᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴀ ᴛʀᴜʟʏ ᴜɴꜰᴏʀɢᴇᴛᴛᴀʙʟᴇ ꜰʀɪᴇɴᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ ᴄᴏɴꜱɪꜱᴛɪɴɢ ᴏꜰ ᴀ ᴡᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ʀᴇᴅ ꜰʟᴀɢ, ᴀ ᴍᴇɴᴀᴄᴇ ᴛᴏ ꜱᴏᴄɪᴇᴛʏ, ᴀ ᴛᴏᴍʙᴏʏ, ᴀ ꜰᴇᴍᴄᴇʟ, ᴀɴ ᴇ-ᴛʜᴏᴛ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ꜱᴄʜɪᴢᴏᴘʜʀᴇɴɪᴄ. ɪᴛ ꜰᴇᴇʟꜱ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴛᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ᴀ ʙᴀᴅ ʙᴀʀ ᴊᴏᴋᴇ, ʏᴇᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ'ꜱ ᴜɴɪQᴜᴇ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛɪᴇꜱ ʙᴏɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴛᴏɢᴇᴛʜᴇʀ ɪɴ ᴜɴɪᴛʏ ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴅᴅ ʟᴏᴏᴋꜱ, ᴏᴄᴄᴀꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ᴊᴀɪʟ ᴠɪꜱɪᴛꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ʙʀᴏᴋᴇɴ ʙᴏɴᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇʏ ᴍᴀʏ ᴇɴᴄᴏᴜɴᴛᴇʀ ᴀʟᴏɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴀʏ. ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴀᴅᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇꜱ ʙʀɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇʀ ᴛᴏɢᴇᴛʜᴇʀ, ꜰᴏʀɢɪɴɢ ᴀ ᴜɴʙʀᴇᴀᴋᴀʙʟᴇ ʙᴏɴᴅ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴅᴇꜰɪᴇꜱ ᴄᴏɴᴠᴇɴᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇᴍʙʀᴀᴄᴇꜱ ᴛʜᴇɪʀ ᴄᴏʟʟᴇᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ꜱᴛʀᴀɴɢᴇɴᴇꜱꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">...ᴀɴᴅ ɴᴏᴡ, ʏᴏᴜ'ʀᴇ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ᴛᴏ ɪɴꜰɪʟᴛʀᴀᴛᴇ ᴀ ᴄᴇʟᴇʙʀɪᴛʏ'ꜱ ɢᴀʟᴀ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ ʟᴇᴀᴅᴇʀꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/0o9HzQ3zAcE?si=G5YjyIS8s6OMhjut\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LSSG9CG.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ob6eBb8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HtF5qFI.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ:<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/taorotana\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/veyonis\" target=\"_blank\">ᴠᴇʏᴏɴɪꜱ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdvM32oV1WvRo7vmcCV521ONVkq9UjCoA2WaZfv226zacBtGw/viewform?usp=dialog\" target=\"_blank\">2025 ʙᴏᴛ ꜱᴜʀᴠᴇʏ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴜᴛʜᴏʀꜱ ɴᴏᴛᴇ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ ʜᴀᴅ ᴛᴏᴏ ᴍᴜᴄʜ ᴅᴀᴍɴ ꜰᴜɴ ᴡʀɪᴛɪɴɢ ᴛꜱ😭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_aa8e417f-fdfa-434e-bc0c-543b941be507.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","⛓️ Dominant","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy","🌗 Switch"],"chats":17776,"messages":313466,"created_at":"2025-01-27T23:22:41.198616+00:00"}